data.description: Welcome to this newly constructed 2021 single-story home! Boasting 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, the master bedroom sits at the front, featuring a spacious walk-in closet and a stunning master bathroom with dual sinks, a walk-in shower, and a separate beautiful tub. The other bedrooms are positioned at the back of the home for privacy.  The modern kitchen comes equipped with stainless steel appliances, and the convenience of a washer and dryer is included. The vinyl-fenced yard provides a private outdoor space. The living room and dining room can be separate or combined, offering flexibility for an office or additional living area.   Located just 15 minutes from the highway, parks, community pools, shopping plazas, restaurants, fitness centers and hospital/urgent care. This home combines comfort and convenience seamlessly, so schedule a tour today to view your future dream home!
